187
00:10:41,525 --> 00:10:43,650
- For whom, sir?
- The all-star team.

188
00:10:46,317 --> 00:10:50,317
"Abbie Hoffman, Tom Hayden, Jerry Rubin,
David Dellinger, Rennie Davis,

189
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:54,150
Lee Weiner, John Froines...
and Bobby Seale?"

190
