210
00:11:55,984 --> 00:11:58,150
- Civil rights activists--
- I know why it was passed.

211
00:11:58,234 --> 00:11:59,775
Why the fuck is he teaching...

212
00:11:59,859 --> 00:12:03,025
It doesn't matter why it was passed.
It matters what it can do.

213
00:12:03,109 --> 00:12:05,900
We're not sure what it can do.
No one's ever been charged with it.

214
00:12:05,984 --> 00:12:07,400
That makes it exciting.

215
00:12:07,484 --> 00:12:10,192
It's like virgin land.
Undeveloped real estate.

216
00:12:10,734 --> 00:12:13,484
- It's a law and they broke it.
- Of course, sir.

217
00:12:13,567 --> 00:12:14,817
- Is there a problem?
- No, sir.

218
00:12:14,900 --> 00:12:17,900
Say what you want to say,
since I'm paying for your wisdom.

219
00:12:17,984 --> 00:12:19,317
Give me my money's worth.

220
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:21,192
Sir, there are people who will see this

221
00:12:21,275 --> 00:12:23,567
