and there were people
who see these men as martyrs.

223
00:12:26,567 --> 00:12:28,859
- Are any of those people in this room?
- No, sir.

224
00:12:28,942 --> 00:12:31,650
You're 33 and you're about
to be named lead prosecutor

225
00:12:31,734 --> 00:12:33,900
in the most important trial
in your lifetime

226
00:12:33,984 --> 00:12:36,859
after being handpicked
by the attorney general.

227
00:12:36,942 --> 00:12:38,775
I'm about to do that right now.

228
00:12:38,859 --> 00:12:42,942
But before I do, let me ask you,
how do you see them?

229
00:12:43,859 --> 00:12:46,150
- Personally or in terms of--
- Personally.

230
00:12:46,234 --> 00:12:48,567
I see them as vulgar, anti-establishment,

231
00:12:48,650 --> 00:12:52,275
