- Evidently not.

515
00:28:44,484 --> 00:28:45,942
You spoke for Bobby.

516
00:28:46,025 --> 00:28:48,442
I made it very clear
that I'm not his lawyer.

517
00:28:48,525 --> 00:28:50,845
- I'd like to sit in on these meetings.
- You can't.

518
00:28:50,900 --> 00:28:52,609
- I think I will anyway.
- Fred--

519
00:28:52,692 --> 00:28:54,942
