534
00:29:34,234 --> 00:29:35,692
Well, keep trying, all right?

535
00:29:37,109 --> 00:29:38,150
We're back.

536
00:29:38,817 --> 00:29:39,817
Let's go.

537
00:29:40,359 --> 00:29:43,650
Jerry, Abbie,
unless you're asked a direct question,

538
00:29:43,734 --> 00:29:46,192
I want you
to keep your mouths shut in that room.

539
00:29:46,275 --> 00:29:48,275
- This is a political trial.
- What?

540
00:29:48,359 --> 00:29:51,859
This is a political trial
that was already decided for us.

541
00:29:52,400 --> 00:29:55,067
Ignoring that reality is just weird to me.

542
00:29:55,150 --> 00:29:58,359
