544
00:30:00,734 --> 00:30:01,817
Okay.

545
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:20,275
Abbie's smarter than you think he is.

546
00:30:22,275 --> 00:30:24,317
Cows are smarter than I think he is.

547
00:30:26,275 --> 00:30:29,025
- S-T-A-H-L.
- What is your occupation?

548
00:30:29,109 --> 00:30:30,859
I am the mayor's administrative officer.

549
00:30:30,942 --> 00:30:36,775
Calling your attention to March 26, 1968.
Did you have a meeting on that day?

550
00:30:36,859 --> 00:30:38,484
- Yes.
- Uh, with whom?

551
00:30:38,567 --> 00:30:41,859
- Mr. Hoffman and Mr. Rubin, is it?
