1748
01:40:44,817 --> 01:40:46,734
- Do you wanna object?
- Objection.

1749
01:40:46,817 --> 01:40:48,650
- Overruled.
- We attract the people

1750
01:40:48,734 --> 01:40:51,025
who have the most to lose
by this war continuing.

1751
01:40:51,109 --> 01:40:53,025
I'm glad you brought that up.
Did you serve?

1752
01:40:53,109 --> 01:40:55,775
I wasn't drafted.
I didn't try to evade the...

1753
01:40:55,859 --> 01:40:58,734
