1767
01:41:41,734 --> 01:41:43,984
Isn't it great to be here in Chicago!

1768
01:41:47,817 --> 01:41:49,942
Come here.
Son of a bitch!

1769
01:41:50,025 --> 01:41:51,317
Hey, leave the kid alone!

1770
01:41:52,317 --> 01:41:53,859
- Hold him!
- Hey!

1771
01:41:53,942 --> 01:41:55,400
Jesus! What is wrong with...

