1776
01:42:01,900 --> 01:42:04,234
Get off of him! Hey! Get the--

1777
01:42:04,317 --> 01:42:07,609
I'd like to say to the cops back there
that we're allowed to be here.

1778
01:42:07,692 --> 01:42:10,109
- We have permits for this.
- And out of nowhere...

1779
01:42:12,317 --> 01:42:15,775
It was six armed police officers versus
Rennie and a pocket protector.

1780
01:42:15,859 --> 01:42:17,400
I can understand that response.

1781
01:42:17,484 --> 01:42:19,525
How about your response? Let's press play.

1782
01:42:20,025 --> 01:42:21,484
We're gonna need medics...

1783
01:42:21,567 --> 01:42:23,442
The whole world is watching.

1784
01:42:23,525 --> 01:42:27,025
The whole world is watching!

1785
01:42:27,525 --> 01:42:29,109
They've just beaten Rennie, Dave.

1786
01:42:29,192 --> 01:42:31,859
Listen. We can still get
everyone out of here safely.

1787
01:42:31,942 --> 01:42:33,234
No, we can't.

1788
01:42:33,317 --> 01:42:36,734
The whole world is watching!

1789
01:42:36,817 --> 01:42:38,609
The whole world is watching!

1790
01:42:39,109 --> 01:42:42,317
Dellinger tried to stop you from saying
what you were about to say.

1791
01:42:42,400 --> 01:42:43,775
Tell them to stay calm.

1792
01:42:45,609 --> 01:42:47,484
- No.
- The whole world is watching!

1793
01:42:47,567 --> 01:42:49,817
- Tom?
- Did you tell 'em to stay calm?

1794
01:42:49,900 --> 01:42:54,942
Wait, Rennie Davis has just been
beaten by the police.

1795
01:42:55,025 --> 01:42:58,484
Rennie's skull has been cracked open.

1796
01:42:58,567 --> 01:43:01,067
- Did you tell your crowd to stay calm--
- Bill--

1797
01:43:01,150 --> 01:43:04,359
I'm Richard Schultz, Tom.
And John Mitchell told me to win.

1798
01:43:04,442 --> 01:43:06,734
Did you tell your crowd
to stay calm or--

1799
01:43:06,817 --> 01:43:08,525
Yes. If blood is gonna flow...

1800
01:43:08,609 --> 01:43:10,900
