1817
01:44:29,025 --> 01:44:31,650
- By an armored division.
- The Illinois National Guard.

1818
01:44:31,734 --> 01:44:32,817
They're the good guys.

1819
01:44:32,900 --> 01:44:35,484
Jeeps fitted with concertina wire
called Daley dozers.

1820
01:44:37,817 --> 01:44:39,692
When did I stop being
