getting the nomination a mile away.

1836
01:45:30,275 --> 01:45:32,035
From the House of Representatives

1837
01:45:32,067 --> 01:45:34,359
who represents the great state of Ohio,

1838
01:45:34,442 --> 01:45:36,525
representative Wayne Hays to the stage.

1839
01:45:36,609 --> 01:45:38,484
Thank you, Mr. Chairman.

1840
01:45:38,567 --> 01:45:41,234
The great state of Ohio,
the Buckeye State--

1841
01:45:41,317 --> 01:45:42,567
The Buckeye State!

1842
