1868
01:47:13,109 --> 01:47:17,900
They had armored vehicles and bayonets!
They took off their name tags and badges!

1869
01:47:17,984 --> 01:47:21,400
We were trying to protest peacefully
at the fucking convention!

1870
01:47:35,692 --> 01:47:37,359
Hands behind your back.

1871
01:47:39,400 --> 01:47:40,442
Yeah.

1872
01:47:42,984 --> 01:47:44,775
