1873
01:47:50,984 --> 01:47:51,984
Our...

1874
01:47:53,192 --> 01:47:54,192
What?

1875
01:47:55,984 --> 01:47:56,984
Our...

1876
01:47:58,484 --> 01:47:59,525
Our blood.

1877
01:48:01,067 --> 01:48:03,692
"Our blood."

1878
01:48:04,859 --> 01:48:06,775
"If our blood is gonna flow..."

